  "texts": [
    "Incorporating mechanisms to validate factual accuracy during the generation process will further enhance the quality of the output.",
    "Additionally, ensuring accurate APA-style citations and referencing is crucial for meeting the standards of academic integrity.",
    "In the meantime, it appears that fears regarding GPT-4 replacing jobs in the near future are unfounded.",
    "GPT-4 cannot currently be used to generate psychology papers with proper APA citations and verifiable information.",
    "Instead, GPT-4 may be better suited for assisting in the planning and editing of human-created writing."
